rows.label: tev016802_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Quentin about FrontierNav.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Quentin to tell you more about data probes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Quentin if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0001
rows.name:
Our current system for expanding FrontierNav is to
display the pre-calculated optimal sites as markers
on the map for data probes to be placed at.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0002
rows.name:
But I understand that some FrontierNav data probe
placement sites can be quite difficult for BLADEs on
the ground to find.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0003
rows.name:
I get lots of requests to pick more accessible placement
sites.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0004
rows.name:
However, I'm already at the end of my rope just trying
to keep FrontierNav up and running. So I wish people
would stop asking for things I can't possibly do![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0007
rows.name:
I mainly do FrontierNav-related system engineering
work, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0008
rows.name:
Day after day after day, I pull overtime, fighting
endless battles with massive volumes of data...
Honestly, I'm at my breaking point.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0009
rows.name:
I mean, sure, I know we civilians aren't out there
putting our lives on the line like BLADE.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0010
rows.name:
And I know we're short handed! I know all of that...
But what's rough is still rough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0011
rows.name:
If this keeps up, I'm going to burn out.
*sigh* I'd better go ask her for advice soon...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0019
rows.name:
Thanks to BLADE's efforts, we've come to understand
a little bit more about Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0020
rows.name:
When we first landed here, we knew next to nothing
about the world outside our walls, and no one was
sure that we'd even be able to survive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0021
rows.name:
That's what spurred us to develop the upgraded,
information-gathering data probes known as "research
probes"â€”and why we made that data viewable to all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0022
rows.name:
Now everyone can use FrontierNav to learn about
Mira, and scientists can put its data to good use
in their research.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0023
rows.name:
It's a major pain to manage the vast quantity of data
the probes are collecting, but at least the value we're
getting out of it makes the trouble worthwhile.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_SEL0051
rows.name: Ask Quentin about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0024
rows.name: So I hear that you and Hope have gotten pretty...close.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0025
rows.name:
You know she belongs to all of us, right?
It isn't fair for you to monopolize her.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0026
rows.name: ...What? SHE approached YOU?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0027
rows.name: Dammit, no! NO! I refuse to accept that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0030
rows.name:
It is always a joy and a pleasure to speak to you,
Hope. Let me thank you again for your wise counsel.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0031
rows.name:
Might I invite you out again today, perhaps?
There's a matter I'd love to get your input on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0032
rows.name:
Er, I'm sorry, but I'm on an important mission today.
I don't think I'd be able to fit that into my schedule.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0033
rows.name:
But if you tell Ornella what's troubling you,
I promise to arrange some time soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0034
rows.name:
It would be my deepest pleasure!
I await word of your availability with bated breath.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_SEL0061
rows.name: Ask Quentin about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0035
rows.name:
Lately, Hope hasn't seemed to be in very high spirits.
I can't imagine what's going on.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0036
rows.name:
And Ornella seems to have disappeared completely!
I wonder what happened...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0037
rows.name:
Hope has been such a huge help to me.
If she needs aid herself, I would do anything for her.
...ANYTHING.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0038
rows.name:
Not that there's something a nobody like me could do
to help an amazing person like her...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0041
rows.name:
Oh, Hope! It's you! I've been meaning to talk to
you because I haven't seen Ornella around lately.
Is everything okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0042
rows.name: O-Ornella? Well, I'm afraid she... Um...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0043
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0044
rows.name:
Oh no! Forgive me, Hope! If it's something difficult
for you to talk about, you don't need to tell me
anything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0045
rows.name:
I'm sure she's just...taking a long vacation!
Yes. That must be it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_SEL0071
rows.name: Ask Quentin about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0046
rows.name:
I did a little hacking to help Hope find what she was
looking for.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0047
rows.name:
But my boss figured out what I'd done and came
down on me like a ton of bricks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0048
rows.name:
Fortunately, he owed Hope a favor or two himself,
so when I told him why I'd done it, he said that he
would have done the same in my position.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0049
rows.name:
Hope really is such an incredible person.
She's like the goddess of New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0052
rows.name: Say, Hope? Do you ever give advice to my...boss?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0053
rows.name:
I only ask because I brought you up the other day,
and he got very excited.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0054
rows.name:
Why yes, Quentin. After we spoke about your working
conditions, I went to your boss in an effort to improve
them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0055
rows.name:
He mentioned that he was having problems with his
mimeosome, so I introduced him to a good
maintenance technician.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0056
rows.name:
Ah, that explains it! Thank you so much!
My boss is still stubborn, but we've been getting along
much better recently, and now I know why.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev016802_MSG0057
rows.name:
I can't thank you enough. I really hope we can talk
like that again sometime.[ST:wait ]
